Title: "Detailed ethnicity"
Description: "The codes for the concepts 'Unknown', 'Asked but no answer', 'other, and the 41 [CDC ethnicity codes](http://www.cdc.gov/phin/resources/vocabulary/index.html) that are grouped under one of the 2 OMB ethnicity category codes."
